OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy for a
OL,6,Ftime as a band of heavy, perhaps
OL,7,Fthundery, showers moves east across
OL,8,Fthe region during the evening. Any
OL,9,Fshowers will become isolated after
OL,10,Fmidnight, with largely clear skies and
OL,11,Flight winds, though remaining widely
OL,12,Fwarm and humid.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTuesday:FAnother dry, hazy day with
OL,15,Fplenty of sunshine and widely hot
OL,16,Ftemperatures. Light winds will offer
OL,17,Flittle relief. A warm and humid night
OL,18,Fto follow.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
